#. <section class="sutta" id="sn2.27"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn2.27:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 2"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 2"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn2.27:0.2"
msgid "3. Nānātitthiyavagga"
msgstr "3. Various Sectarians"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn2.27:0.3"
msgid "27. Nandasutta"
msgstr "27. With Nanda"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn2.27:1.1"
msgid ""
"Ekamantaṃ ṭhito kho nando devaputto bhagavato santike imaṃ gāthaṃ abhāsi:"
msgstr ""
"Standing to one side, the god Nanda recited this verse in the Buddha’s "
"presence:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="pts1ed" id="pts1ed1.63"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn2.27:2.1"
msgid "“Accenti kālā tarayanti rattiyo,"
msgstr "“Time flies, nights pass by,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.27:2.2"
msgid "Vayoguṇā anupubbaṃ jahanti;"
msgstr "the stages of life leave us one by one."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.27:2.3"
msgid "Etaṃ bhayaṃ maraṇe pekkhamāno,"
msgstr "Seeing this peril in death,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.27:2.4"
msgid "Puññāni kayirātha sukhāvahānī”ti."
msgstr "you should do good deeds that bring happiness.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.146"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn2.27:3.1"
msgid "“Accenti kālā tarayanti rattiyo,"
msgstr "“Time flies, nights pass by,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.27:3.2"
msgid "Vayoguṇā anupubbaṃ jahanti;"
msgstr "the stages of life leave us one by one."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.27:3.3"
msgid "Etaṃ bhayaṃ maraṇe pekkhamāno,"
msgstr "Seeing this peril in death,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.27:3.4"
msgid "Lokāmisaṃ pajahe santipekkho”ti."
msgstr "one looking for peace would drop the world’s bait.”"
